posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'Here at Dove Tree, our one, two and three bedrooms feature convenience, quality and professional management, and proper maintenance.', 'Our residents always come first!', 'We offer paid utilities such as heat, water, trash, sewer, and recycling.', 'Our apartment homes have tons of closet space, a dishwasher, electric range, and a ceiling fan in the dining room.', 'Call today to schedule your tour and see all we have to offer for yourself!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Utilities Included : Heat, Water, Sewer & Trash Removal Services', '- Unique Floor Plans', '- Adjoining Dining Room', 'And Living Room Area', '- Standard Dominium Comfort Package', '- Ample Counter Top & Cabinet Space', '- Handicapped Accessible Homes (select homes)', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Dove Tree participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-4:00PM', 'Call today to schedule your tour:', 'show contact info', 'Dove Tree', '1105 Lions Park Drive', 'Elk River, MN, 55330', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'amdt0SFPW47q']
